msgstr "จัดเรียงโพสต์"

#: App/Controllers/Admin/Posts/ReOrderPosts.php:186 App/Controllers/Admin/Settings/MultisiteSettings.php:159
#: App/Controllers/Admin/Settings/Settings.php:98
msgid "Are you sure?"
msgstr "คุณแน่ใจหรือไม่?"

#: App/Controllers/Admin/Posts/ReOrderPosts.php:187
msgid "Are you sure to doing this? (This may slow down your server if you have too many posts.)"
msgstr "คุณแน่ใจหรือไม่ที่จะทำสิ่งนี้? (นี่อาจทำให้เซิร์ฟเวอร์ของคุณทำงานช้าลงถ้าคุณมีโพสต์จำนวนมาก.)"

#: App/Controllers/Admin/Posts/ReOrderPosts.php:188 App/Views/admin/Settings/multisiteSettings_v.php:17
#: App/Views/admin/Settings/settings_v.php:18
